Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都待著沒動過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真夠高雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐我也想這麼悠閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在酒店做運動也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過請勿口出穢言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是你想得太複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  莉多薇亞真色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是等著也真夠嗆的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當麻當麻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡賣的水果果汁我好想喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才才吃過午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣暴飲暴食會長胖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不會長胖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是沒察覺的情況下  防禦力悄然上升了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你那麼不相信  就量一下我的肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能隨身帶軟尺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西用不著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在要抱住的瞬間避開人家好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  又去給那位男生…不  類人猿加油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了告訴我母親比賽的程序改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過此刻就在那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是喜得貴子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成已經感覺到嬰兒在踢肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  死色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧索拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過別在圖書館吃鬆餅了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這些是天草式的諸位做了給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別掉餅乾屑下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:06:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們挺習慣這裡的生活了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就是專門解讀暗號的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的情報的處理都是我的長項
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉小姐  我也很擅長解讀暗號哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  報告書的數據稍後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋我不是說過  別再掉餅乾屑了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  必要之惡教會什麼時候變得那麼圓滑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,358)\fs21}Necessarius
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市所有的露天場所都是全天全面禁煙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽說過二手煙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼你還繼續點上新的煙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  認真點聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快往這裡看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萌老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是逃脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一些麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…姬神你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這種東西一定要沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快老實點交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個用不著去阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿上  有動靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在三分鐘之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在位於第五學區的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鐵的西部山站發現了歐麗安娜的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史提爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  帶著他去車站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬神  接下來的就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊小姬神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須避開多餘的麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史提爾快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩站
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在英國圖書館找到的關於使徒十字的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,358)\fs21}Croce di Pietro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道些什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單憑口述說明很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接把數據傳到你的手機上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意我怎麼看得懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土御門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自律巴士塞在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離這裡有多遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用跑的得用十分鐘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼久的話  就會被她離開追蹤範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史提爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我通過手機指示  你能畫出理派四陣的圖陣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對東方術式一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  對西洋魔術的追蹤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果會還用得著找你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全超出我的專業範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理派四陣由我展開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我會通過手機告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這身體再使用魔術沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是使用各種魔術的專家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想知道大姐姐我在哪兒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來  該怎麼行動好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬神？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說不上是煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上條他看起來有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是單純為接下來的比賽著急而已嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那種感覺有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種神經兮兮的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是光是比賽的話  應該不至於會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單地說小姬神很在意小上條嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得應該避免用這種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟上條沒那麼要好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦引起別的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會給上條惹麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬神  看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜間巡遊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的學園都市的掛燈和鐳射光線都會亮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很是漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不試著邀請小上條嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣的人突然邀請他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上條也肯定會不知所措的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不適合我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要小姬神覺得高興的事去邀請小上條一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小上條就是這樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不請就是不請
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼那麼固執啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我就不請他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然改變了動向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在往西北方向移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能用「赤之式」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用那招就得把理派四陣給停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就無法追蹤歐麗安娜的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向保持西北
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方打算以直線距離甩開追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離探查有效範圍邊緣還有一千七百米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  突然改變方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼了突然加快速度了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土御門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被算計了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐麗安娜並不知道要走到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能從理派四陣的有效範圍當中逃離出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  將位於術式中心的土御門擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要趕緊才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪兒走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是土御門那了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我才問你那是在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道他到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆警惕可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你能察覺大姐姐我所在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說大姐姐我也能感覺到你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來最危險  所以我來收拾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「背後捅人刀」  記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,358)\fs21}Fallere825
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的魔法名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名為「擔任基礎者」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(384,358)\fs21}Basis104
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已報上了名號  就容我送你一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣粗暴的年輕氣質  大姐姐我也並不討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極力地避免使用魔術  是你的作風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真如此  你會死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是大姐姐我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像張開結界這樣的策略還是會想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會來救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切開始的信號在此  伴隨著耀眼的光芒與尖銳的聲音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\3c&HFF0000&}沉浸在安詳中的渣滓們  不想死就馬上給我醒來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界被化解了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來…是連我都能擊破的結界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟外表不同  看來是能夠進行劇烈運動的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的情況傳不出去我會很苦惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便追著大姐姐我的那兩個人來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為必要之惡教會的成員有多少人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(295,358)\fs21}Necessarius
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我會信這種話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「符文玉章」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原為針對目標使其產生幻覺的靈裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過用法也可以隨機應變…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信術式？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已得知刺突杭劍並不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,358)\fs21}Stab Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說已經沒有讓她待命的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是神裂火織
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒想過聖人會在日本的可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  在學園都市裡有神裂火織私下的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便不慎暴露了  也不會惹出多大的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還垂死掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正追蹤術式已經破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且繼續跟麻煩的小伙糾纏讓自己受傷的話  也很無聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神裂火織的登場…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…像「符文玉章」這麼荒謬的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧她還能信以為真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來再用一次…理派四陣有點困難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是土御門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想歐麗安娜現在應該正從這裡離開才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我稍微嚇唬了對方一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是離御土門所在隧道最近的地鐵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒人跟著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使徒十字的準備還早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(295,358)\fs21}Croce di Pietro
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考一下針對聖人的術式的方案  也挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬神  不抄近路接下來的比賽就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萌老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真幹得出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大姐姐我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是比較擔心你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬神衣服濕透了都看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萌老師胸部的一些地方也濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾特十字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要之惡教會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(351,358)\fs21}Necessarius
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬神？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  小姬神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這裡最近的搭乘點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在北面三百米處的自律巴士站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三百米啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萌老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小上條
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  到底發生什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  這裡發生了什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撞到了一個女性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只見那個人一下子繃緊臉突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歐麗安娜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她為什麼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有襲擊姬神的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個「移動教會」的靈裝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很特別的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她誤以為她是跟禁書目錄同等級的魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其判作為追兵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤以為？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓姬神傷成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由就是認錯人了而已嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}自此  此處將化作吾之藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(351,327)\fs21\fad(600,0)}T   P   I   M   I   M   S   P   F   T
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經叫好救護車了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在小路的入口等著才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡不會被人發覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們的錯  她才被捲進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能就這樣丟下不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又能做些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自以為是了  你這外行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這個受傷的少女我們沒什麼能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們現在能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有追上歐麗安娜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想保護誰的話就攥起拳頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的右手只有將幻想消滅的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上哪有保護幻想的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為這股怒氣只屬於你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小修女的時候就是靠這發揮了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼小姬神還沒恢復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在說夜間巡遊的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:20:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像將用水桶把海裡的水撈上來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要在「盆景」裡將劃分出來的區域設定出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上條當麻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去追歐麗安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  難道說你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抱太大的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也並不在行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用這個人腦海裡禁書目錄的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行最低限度的應急措施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想所有的事情都能完美解決
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跨過這裡吧  上條當麻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史提爾  姬神就拜託給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起姬神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在夜間巡遊之前回到你的病房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你一定要等著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:22:02.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}からまった運命も変えていけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:22:02.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糾纏在一起的命運也是能夠改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:08.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}すべてはこの手の中にある
